<div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
            <h5 class="modal-title">로그인</h5>
            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
            </button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
            <p id="login-message" style="display: none; color:red;">아이디 또는 비밀번호가 일치하지 않습니다.</p>
            <form>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="id-login">아이디</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="id-login" placeholder="아이디">
                    <div class="invalid-feedback">아이디를 입력해주세요.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="pwd-login">비밀번호</label>
                    <input type="password" class="form-control" id="pwd-login" placeholder="비밀번호">
                    <div class="invalid-feedback">비밀번호를 입력해주세요.</div>
                </div>

                <div class="custom-control custom-switch">
                    <input type="checkbox" class="custom-control-input" id="reserve-login">
                    <label class="custom-control-label" for="reserve-login">자동 로그인</label>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    구아바 플레이트 계정이 없으시다면<br>
                    지금 바로 <a id="modal-btn-regist" href="#">회원가입</a>을 진행해주세요!
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
            <button type="button" id="btn-login-user" class="btn btn-primary">로그인</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>